                        <interp inst="t18390304-name-820" type="given" value="RALPH"></interp>RALPH WOODWARD</persName>
                  </hi>. I am servant to the prosecutor. On the 5th of March I met the prisoner, about twelve doors down New Gloucester-street, with the handkerchief tied round his neck—I did not know him before—I know the handkerchief well, as I often wear it at night when I go out—the prisoner said he had bought it the day before.</p>
